## Accessibility

### WCAG 2.1 AA Compliance

**Color Contrast**:
- Text: 4.5:1 minimum against background
- Large text (18px+): 3:1 minimum
- Interactive elements: Clear visual distinction

**Focus States**:
```css
*:focus-visible {
  @apply outline-2 outline-offset-2 outline-primary-600;
}
```

**Semantic HTML**:
- Use proper heading hierarchy (h1 → h2 → h3)
- Use `<button>` for clickable actions (not `<div>`)
- Use `<a>` for navigation (not `<button>`)
- Use `<nav>`, `<main>`, `<article>` for structure

**ARIA Labels**:
- All interactive elements have accessible names
- Images have alt text (descriptive or empty)
- Form inputs have associated labels

**Keyboard Navigation**:
- All interactive elements are keyboard accessible
- Tab order is logical
- Skip links for main content

**Motion**:
```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  * {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
  }
}
```

